overview: In a sequel to Johnny Harden and the Champs, Sky Dawson is out on the water again and he still can't keep his hands to himself. He and Dick Fisk suck and rim each other with zeal until Sky throws his legs in the air and Dick takes the plunge. Dick puts his dick in Sky's mouth and then Sky turns it around and comes onto Dick's open face.
title: Champs: The Finals
